nt" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig09c">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig10a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig10a.jpeg" height="772" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 10a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig10a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig10b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig10b.jpeg" height="739" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 10b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig10b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig11a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig11a.jpeg" height="889" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 11a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig11a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig11b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig11b.jpeg" height="858" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 11b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig11b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig12a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig12a.jpeg" height="914" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 12a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig12a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig12b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig12b.jpeg" height="910" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 12b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig12b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig12c" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig12c.jpeg" height="767" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 12c</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig12c">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig12d" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig12d.jpeg" height="879" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 12d</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig12d">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig13" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig13.jpeg" height="1280" width="1049" aria-labelledby="fig13" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 13</span> Splenic torsion. Coronal contrast-enhanced CT image shows an enlarged, inferiorly displaced, poorly enhancing spleen (*). Heterogeneous enhancement of the splenic vein (arrow) is suggestive of associated thrombosis.<div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig13">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig14" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig14.jpeg" height="971" width="1280" aria-labelledby="fig14" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 14</span> Splenic torsion with a twisted pedicle. Transverse contrast-enhanced CT image reveals a twisted vascular pedicle in the splenic hilum (arrow) and a nonenhancing spleen. Associated free fluid and mesenteric edema also are seen.<div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig14">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig15a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig15a.jpeg" height="919" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 15a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig15a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig15b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig15b.jpeg" height="997" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 15b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig15b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig16a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig16a.jpeg" height="843" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 16a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig16a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig16b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig16b.jpeg" height="781" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 16b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig16b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig17a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig17a.jpeg" height="1026" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 17a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig17a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig17b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig17b.jpeg" height="943" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 17b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig17b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig18" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig18.jpeg" height="887" width="1280" aria-labelledby="fig18" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 18</span> Epiploic appendagitis. Transverse contrast-enhanced CT image shows an ovoid lesion with overall attenuation of fat and a surrounding rimlike region of hyperattenuation (arrow). The close association of the lesion with the colon in the left lower quadrant is suggestive of the diagnosis.<div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig18">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig19" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig19.jpeg" height="954" width="1280" aria-labelledby="fig19" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 19</span> Epiploic appendagitis. Magnified transverse contrast-enhanced CT image shows the characteristic location and appearance of a twisted epiploic appendage (arrow) with a central dot sign.<div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig19">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig20a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig20a.jpeg" height="830" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 20a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig20a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig20b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig20b.jpeg" height="843" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 20b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig20b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig21a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig21a.jpeg" height="1085" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 21a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig21a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig21b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig21b.jpeg" height="1280" width="1115" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 21b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig21b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig22a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.331125016/asset/images/125016fig22a.jpeg" height="717" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 22a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.331125016&amp;id=fig22a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div